window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Leverage the tools, strategies, and secrets of rental properties, affiliate marketing, dropshipping, Amazon FBA, blogging, and 20+ more ways to quit your job and become rich.</p> <p>It rarely happens that people fall into wealth by chance. Though we are taught not to have an unhealthy love for money, it is also true that there is a cost to living. It may be that you must rethink your budget repeatedly because you must take every dime you spend into consideration. Perhaps you have a desperate need for a holiday, which for so long has eluded you. Or there might be other things you want, or need, but you are just unable to afford them. If you are thinking about gaining extra income, there are opportunities out there waiting just for you! Also, some of the methods you can use to obtain an extra stream of income require minimal resources yet can really boost your revenue.</p> <p>You may have heard about passive income; however, you are also unsure of what it really is. Do not worry, <i>Passive Income Ideas: A Beginnerâ€™s Guide to Building Multiple Streams, Sources, and Business Strategies to Create Real Wealth and Long-Term Financial Freedom</i> has got you covered! We will examine several options that are available to boost your revenue.</p> <p>Passive income may begin small, where not a lot of profit is made, but as you progress, your endeavors will grow, and so will your stream of passive income. Many people start with passive income streams to gain extra revenue along with their normal salaries; however, some people have turned to passive income as their primary source of revenue. We will have an in-depth look at the top 10 methods to gain passive income, including step-by-step instructions.</p> <p>This audiobook promises to be a handy tool in growing your revenue, and in providing many possibilities for combining different sources of passive income to suit your needs best.</p>"; 
